{
  "texts": [
    "In other words, the \"proportion\" of non-AEs in the infinite set of perturbed inputs.",
    "To evaluate PR, one of the earliest works Webb et al. (2019) introduced a useful black-box statistical estimator, especially for cases where PR is very high.",
    "Later, more efficient white-box statistical estimators were proposed in TIT et al. (2023).",
    "Additionally, PR has been extended to applications such as explainable AI Huang et al. (2023) and text-to-image models Zhang et al. (2024b).",
    "For an overview of PR estimators, we refer readers to Zhao (2025)."
  ]
}